lyrics:
[Verse]
In the wild, wild West, they rode side by side
Two cowboys in love, hearts open wide
But fate had a different plan, they couldn't foresee
For Jone found another man, leaving Strongheart sadly

[Chorus]
I found another man, a love that feels so true
But the echoes of your touch still haunt me through and through
I'll cherish our memories, our love's sweet embrace
But now I've found another man, a new path I will trace
